message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this amazing product! I think you'll really love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $110.
Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the product, but I'm looking to keep my expenses down. Could you consider selling it to me for $95?
Hi Bob, I understand your concern about expenses, but I'm not willing to go as low as $95. I'm willing to meet you halfway and sell it to you for $105.
